Package: balance-daemon
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, balance
Description: Init scripts for balance
 Scripts and configuration files to run the balance TCP proxy as a
 daemon in the background. This makes it easier to run it in a
 standard, permanent configuration.
